    "name": "step",
    "purpose": "Owns the step protocol split into per-type files: StepKind with Model(ModelStepKind)/Execution(ExecutionStepKind)/User(UserStepKind) sub-kinds where ExecutionStepKind::Invocation carries an ExecutionRequest (kind.rs), the StepSignature record carrying task/step_no/name/kind with StepSignature::new(task, step_no, name, kind) preserving the caller-supplied TaskSignature, the StepEvent stream enum with Started/Update/Complete/Fail where Complete and Fail carry a StepResult (event.rs), the StepResult content payload (result.rs), the StepStatus lifecycle enum Prepare/Process/Complete/Fail (status.rs), and the StepPreview signature+result record (preview.rs); mod.rs is re-export wiring only.",
